Sentencas: The introduction of catalyst on anode of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) has been an effective way to alleviate the carbon deposition when utilizing biogas as the fuel.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: A series of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-delta (x = 0, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) oxides are synthesized by sol-gel method and used as catalysts precursors for biogas dry reforming.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: The phase structure of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-delta oxides before and after reduction are characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: The texture properties, carbon deposition, CH4 and CO2 conversion rate of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-delta catalysts are evaluated and compared.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: The peak power density of 739 mW cm-2 is obtained by a commercial SOFC with La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-delta catalyst at 850 & DEG;C when using a mixture of CH4: CO2 = 2:1 as fuel.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: This shows a great improvement from the cell without catalyst for internal dry reforming, which is attributed to the formation of NiCo alloy active species after reduction in H2 atmosphere.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: The results indicate the benefits of inhibiting the carbon deposition on Ni-based anode through introducing the La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-delta-catalyst precursor.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming

Sentencas: Additionally, the dry reforming technology will also help to convert part of the exhaust heat into chemical energy and improve the efficiency of SOFC system with biogas fuel.
Titulo: Investigation of La0.6Sr0.4Co1-xNixO3-d (x1/40, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) catalysts on solid oxide fuel cells anode for biogas dry reforming
